{"tid":1596570,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"apple喂屎都搶住食，這6個理由告訴你：為什麼iPhone11不值得購買","createTime":"2019-09-26T14:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T01:05:40.000Z","uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d83f3f69198dd2eede5d7692186b0cdb87a1ca04","tid":1596570,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:25:41.000Z","msg":"外觀<br />\n<br />\n和iPhone XR相比，iPhone11的邊框和劉海沒有任何明顯的提升和變窄。當你戴上黑色保護殼時，寬邊框帶來的衝擊力請自行腦補。Face ID也沒有明顯升級，依舊不支援橫置識別。一句話總結：iPhone11和iPhone XR屏幕邊框和劉海屏大小保持一致。沒有區別和升級。<br />\n<br />\n快充<br />\n<br />\n在快充方面，iPhone11依舊沒有明顯的提升：有線充電功率最高為22.5W左右，無線充電功率為7.5W左右。遠遠落後於Android旗艦手機的快充方案。目前Android陣營的有線快充為50W和即將發佈的65W，無線充電功率可以達到30W左右<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20190926/5/43/2/這6個理由告訴你-為什麼iPhone11不值得購買-10660965.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20190926%2F5%2F43%2F2%2F%E9%80%996%E5%80%8B%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1%E5%91%8A%E8%A8%B4%E4%BD%A0-%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BCiPhone11%E4%B8%8D%E5%80%BC%E5%BE%97%E8%B3%BC%E8%B2%B7-10660965.html&d=0M2zeZ419d%2BEsiU1FPoAw82proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=4da6120f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20190926/5/43/2/這6個理由告訴你-為什麼iPhone11不值得購買-10660965.html</a>。"},{"pid":"0366e979669573f9cbfdeb790ef1fe21b83ee98d","tid":1596570,"uid":12628,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:27:21.000Z","msg":"講得好，我就是信sina<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11354eba227eb74d7ee494cd349afb61e5883075","tid":1596570,"uid":25538,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:28:34.000Z","msg":"咁買pro"},{"pid":"0b7c84aca4c5d87c916bf850f4b2e6a413acc2a9","tid":1596570,"uid":134226,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:30:57.000Z","msg":"唔通買屎為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces